api_list.name: Get Top NFT Collections
api_list.description: Get the NFT collections ordered by volume or sales.

optional_parameters.name: period
optional_parameters.description: Can be `24h` for 24 hours, `7d` for 7 days, `30d` for 30 days, or `all` for all time. Default is `all`

optional_parameters.name: sortBy
optional_parameters.description: How collections are sorted. Can be `volume`, `sales`, `floorPrice`, `averagePrice`, or `marketCap`. Default is `volume`

optional_parameters.name: offset
optional_parameters.description: For pagination. Number of collections offset from the beginning of the result list.

optional_parameters.name: network
optional_parameters.description: Can be `Ethereum`, `BNB Chain`, `Polygon`, `Arbitrum`, `Optimism`, `Solana`, or `null` for all top collections comparing all the above networks.

optional_parameters.name: limit
optional_parameters.description: For pagination. Maximum number of contracts to return. Default is `20`, max is `100`.
